<normalizedToken id="A5FE081A912182AEC2C3866D92A48F50" originalValue="flügelförmigen" pageId="null" pageNumber="245">fluegelfoermigen</normalizedToken>
Rand.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CB31A542E5B5590BFD410E93D43C5752" pageId="null" pageNumber="245">
Die Gattung 
